net/mlx5: Use first online CPU instead of hard coded CPU

Hard coded CPU (0 in our case) might be offline. Hence, use the first
online CPU instead.

Fixes: f891b7cdbdcd ("net/mlx5: Enable single IRQ for PCI Function")
